          setSyncStatus("лҸҷкё°нҷ”: мҠӨмјҖмӨ„ л¶Ҳлҹ¬мҳӨлҠ” мӨ‘вҖҰ (лҚ°мқҙн„° л§Һмңјл©ҙ 30мҙҲ~1л¶„ кұёлҰҙ мҲҳ мһҲмқҢ)", "warn", {
            pinMs: 120000,
            force: true
          });
          await pullWithRetryUntilSuccess(() => pullSchedulesFromSupabaseAndApply());
          setSyncStatus("лҸҷкё°нҷ”: мһ…кёҲВ·нҡҢм°Ёк¶ҢВ·кё°нғҖ л¶Ҳлҹ¬мҳӨлҠ” мӨ‘вҖҰ", "warn", { pinMs: 120000, force: true });
          await pullWithRetryUntilSuccess(() => pullPaymentsFromSupabaseAndApply());
          await pullCouponPassesFromSupabaseAndApply();
          await pullDayoffRequestsFromSupabaseAndApply();
          await pullSubmissionReceiptsFromSupabaseAndApply();
          await pullSharedLimitConfigAndApply();
